<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA71">
<l>iṉiniṉṟu niṉperumai yāṉuraippa teṉṉē</l>
<l>taṉiniṉṟa cārvilā mūrtti paṉinī</l>
<l>rakattulavu ceñcaṭaiyā ṉākattā ṉāṉku</l>
<l>mukattāṉiṉ ṉunti mutal.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing here now what shall I tell about your greatness?</l>
<l>Form without support who stands alone, the one of red matted hair</l>
<l>with the dewy water moving inside is in [your] body, the one</l>
<l>with four faces [has his] origin in your navel.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
